QuestData.Title: Return to Thalodien
QuestData.Description: It would be best if this information got back to Thalodien as soon as possible. I'll stay here and cover our tracks.$B$BIt wouldn't do us much good to have Kael'thas find out what we were snooping around here. Secret information is always better if your enemy doesn't know you have it.
QuestData.LogDescription: Return to Spymaster Thalodien at Area 52 in Netherstorm.
QuestData.RewardText: You do not cease to amaze me, $n. That was quite the feat of stealth you pulled off at Manaforge Coruu.
